{"title":"迎来新世纪第一轮太阳","authors":["孙友田"],"dates":[{"year":2001,"month":1,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎来新世纪第一轮太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孙友田"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乘着改革的大潮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏着隆冬的冰霜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎来新世纪第一轮太阳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泰山群峰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"映出它第一抹亮丽的色彩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄河水系，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪耀它第一道奇特的金黄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万里长城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"逶迤它第一缕美妙的霞光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"2001·1·1"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公元二十一世纪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从波涛汹涌的大海上升起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红红火火，圆圆满满，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无比辉煌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切从新开始，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开始于晨光熹微的黎明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开始于云蒸霞蔚的东方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第九个五年计划胜利完成，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光又洒满"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新的起跑线上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"加快发展的“十五”计划，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像一组威武的舰队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在历史的黄金水道上起航。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"改革开放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"激活一江春水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百舸竞发，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扑向蔚蓝的海洋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一座桥梁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都意味着跨越，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一个港口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都聚集着希望。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一朵浪花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都展现中国人的微笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一滴海水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都跃动新世纪的太阳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从沸腾的东海岸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向西部遥望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丰富而又贫瘠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"壮美而又荒凉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开发大西北！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史的重任"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"落在我们肩上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"交通，向西延伸钢铁的动脉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水利，向西喷吐润泽的诗行。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"电网，撒下透明的珠串，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建筑，举起强劲的臂膀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天山牧歌要唱绿荒漠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九曲黄河要浇灌小康。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风锤在石壁上演奏华夏动人的乐章。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机组在煤层内试刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雕塑西部的风光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田野盛开科技之花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春意融融，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"厂矿闪烁科技之光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春风荡漾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饱满的麦穗，转动的齿轮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都迸发时代的锋芒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渔姑用金线结出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捕捞富裕的大网，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"织女用银梭织就"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流光溢彩的富强。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌手放开五音，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"画家挥洒七彩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让新世纪有声有色。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"培育人才的希望工程，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拔地而起的高楼大厦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让新世纪英姿飒爽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有生命的都振奋了："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雄狮、蛟龙、向往……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有翅膀的都腾飞了："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大鹏、铁鹰、理想……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我们手挽手齐声欢唱："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我们的队伍向太阳。”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}